defaultThe regulations and stand
defaultards established by national Government are a key means of raising the environmental performance of new housing and improving people’s local quality of life.  Sustainable Homes welcomes this opportunity to contribute to the continuing review of housing standards.  
default&#xa0;
default1.2.
default&#xa0; 
defaultAs the leading provider of training, research, consultancy and benchmarking for social housing providers in the environmental performance of new and existing homes we have both expert and practical experience
default to inform the review. 
